    A Java representation of a Keyword content type. Example Json:

    "__metadata": {
      "uri": "http://127.0.0.1:8080/cd_webservice/odata.svc/Keywords(PublicationId=1,Id=2)",

    },
    "Id": 123,
    "PublicationId": 1,
    "TaxonomyId": 123,
    "Title": "A title",
    "Description": "A description",
    "HasChildren": false,
    "Abstract": false,
    "Navigable": false,
    "Key": "A key",
    "Depth": 0,
    "ItemType": 1,
    "TotalRelatedItems": 1,
    "Components": {
      "__deferred": {
          "uri": "http://127.0.0.1:8080/cd_webservice/odata.svc/Keywords(Id=2,PublicationId=1)/Components"
